OL,3,CGirl was swept out to sea as she posed
OL,4,Cfor photos, inquest hears
OL,6,FA 15-year-old girl was swept out to
OL,7,Fsea "in a blink" as she posed for
OL,8,Fphotos with her friend in front of a
OL,9,Fraging sea, an inquest has heard.
OL,11,FGrace Keeling, from Sutton-in-
OL,12,FAshfield, Nottinghamshire, died in the
OL,13,Fsea at Withernsea, East Yorkshire,
OL,14,Falong with her mother, Sarah Keeling,
OL,15,Fon 2 January.
OL,17,FLocal man Mark Ratcliffe, 67, who went
OL,18,Finto the water to help, also drowned.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
