PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779991869
OL,3,CGirl was swept out to sea as she posed
OL,4,Cfor photos, inquest hears
OL,6,FAn inquest on Thursday heard how Mr
OL,7,FRatcliffe's grandchildren "will grow
OL,8,Fup knowing their granddad was a hero".
OL,10,FRecording a verdict of misadventure in
OL,11,FGrace's case, coroner Lorraine Harris
OL,12,Fsaid: "Grace and her friend were doing
OL,13,Fwhat all teenage girls do ` having fun
OL,14,Fand taking photos.
OL,16,F"Without appreciating the danger of
OL,17,Fgoing so close to the water's edge,
OL,18,FGrace stood with her back to the sea.
OL,26,@oD@[OUpD@eO]tD@GOUxD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779991869
OL,3,CGirl was swept out to sea as she posed
OL,4,Cfor photos, inquest hears
OL,6,F"What happened next was so quick that
OL,7,Fshe would not have had any time to
OL,8,Fhelp herself.
OL,10,F"She was engulfed by a wave and taken
OL,11,Fout to sea."
OL,13,FThe coroner recorded narrative
OL,14,Fverdicts in respect of Mrs Keeling and
OL,15,FMr Ratcliffe.
OL,17,FMrs Keeling, who was 45, had "died in
OL,18,Fpursuit of trying to save her
OL,19,Fdaughter", Ms Harris said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUsD@LO]yD@^OU{D@IO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/11
