OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779991869
OL,3,CGirl was swept out to sea as she posed
OL,4,Cfor photos, inquest hears
OL,6,FOf Mr Ratcliffe she added: "I find
OL,7,Fthat he placed trying to save the
OL,8,Flives of Mrs Keeling and her daughter
OL,9,FGrace over his own safety.
OL,11,F"It was an act of bravery."
OL,13,FThe inquest in Hull heard evidence
OL,14,Ffrom Grace's friend, who had gone with
OL,15,Fthe Keelings to Withernsea for a day
OL,16,Fout.
OL,26,@nD@\OUsD@AOUsD@[O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/11
