OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779991869
OL,3,CGirl was swept out to sea as she posed
OL,4,Cfor photos, inquest hears
OL,6,FIn her evidence, which was summarised
OL,7,Fin a police officer's statement, the
OL,8,Fgirl, who cannot be named, described
OL,9,Fhow she and Grace had been taking
OL,10,Fturns to go down steps from the
OL,11,Fpromenade while the other took photos
OL,12,Fand videos with the sea spray behind.
OL,14,FThe girl said: "We were laughing and
OL,15,Ftaking videos of each other."
OL,17,FShe said they had agreed to "do it one
OL,18,Flast time" and described how she
OL,19,Fwalked about four steps up from Grace,
OL,20,Fwho had her back to the sea.
OL,26,@vD@POUwD@]O]zD@JO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779991869
OL,3,CGirl was swept out to sea as she posed
OL,4,Cfor photos, inquest hears
OL,6,FThe teenager said she turned her back
OL,7,Fon her friend for a moment as Grace
OL,8,Fwas near some railings on the steps
OL,9,Fdown from the Pier Towers landmark.
OL,11,FShe said: "I turned round and, in like
OL,12,Fa split second, Grace was gone.
OL,14,F"It happened as quick as a blink.
OL,16,F"I initially thought she was hiding
OL,17,Fsomewhere."
OL,19,FThe girl said: "Grace was screaming
OL,20,Ffor help."
OL,26,@sD@KOUvD@AOUxD@AOUyD@KO]{D@POU|D@JO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/11
