OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779991869
OL,3,CGirl was swept out to sea as she posed
OL,4,Cfor photos, inquest hears
OL,6,FShe explained how she also began
OL,7,Fscreaming, adding: "The wave came out
OL,8,Fof nowhere."
OL,10,FThe teenager said Mrs Keeling arrived
OL,11,Fand was "freaking out" and screaming
OL,12,Ffor other people to help.
OL,14,FShe explained how Grace's mum went
OL,15,Finto the water.
OL,17,FThe girl said: "Sarah never made it to
OL,18,FGrace because of the waves."
OL,26,@oD@TOUpD@LO]sD@IOUsD@VO]yD@POUzD@\O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/11
