PN,36208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779991869
OL,3,CGirl was swept out to sea as she posed
OL,4,Cfor photos, inquest hears
OL,6,FShe said: "The waves did not stop. It
OL,7,Fwas getting worse. One minute Grace
OL,8,Fwas near the wall and next she was
OL,9,Fgone."
OL,11,FThe teenager said a "huge wave came
OL,12,Fand Sarah was gone".
OL,14,FShe said: "I didn't know what to do. I
OL,15,Fwas screaming 'my friend's in there'."
OL,26,@nD@KOUqD@FO]sD@UOUtD@SO]vD@KOUwD@fO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/11
