FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779991869
OL,3,CGirl was swept out to sea as she posed
OL,4,Cfor photos, inquest hears
OL,6,FThe inquest heard how Mr Ratcliffe's
OL,7,Fand Mrs Keeling's bodies were
OL,8,Frecovered the same afternoon as the
OL,9,Fcoastguard, RNLI, firefighters and
OL,10,Fmore than 100 police officers arrived
OL,11,Fat the scene.
OL,13,FThe search for Grace's body took 13
OL,14,Fdays and she was eventually found
OL,15,Ftrapped among large boulders used for
OL,16,Fsea defences to the south of the
OL,17,Fincident.
OL,19,FThe court heard how at least three
OL,20,Fother people went into the water to
OL,21,Ftry to help.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
