OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779991869
OL,3,CGirl was swept out to sea as she posed
OL,4,Cfor photos, inquest hears
OL,6,FCoroner Lorraine Harris was told about
OL,7,Fthe two-day operation to extract
OL,8,FGrace's remain from the boulders as
OL,9,Femergency services and a construction
OL,10,Ffirm with heavy equipment battled poor
OL,11,Fweather and the tides.
OL,13,FThe hearing was told the sea was too
OL,14,Frough to launch a lifeboat and one
OL,15,Ffisherman with 40 years' experience,
OL,16,Fwho witnessed the incident, said the
OL,17,Fwaves were 12ft (4m) high and the
OL,18,Fconditions were among the worst he had
OL,19,Fseen.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
